text: <Hit> sagð, þæt ða geforewritu cyðað be þara haligra martira lyfe, þæt heora behatu wæron trume to þam sygefestan Criste and heora gewinn and campdom hyg welwillendlice geendodon and timbrunge þæs fullan geleafan hyg on him sylfum fæste geheoldon and þone deaðes wæg myd <ealle> forhogedon and þæt æce rice myd fulfræmednisse hym sylfum geearnodon.
Amang þam wæs ðe eadiga and se halga Quintinus gewilnigende, þæt he þam heofonlican Criste hys gewinnu and his haligan <drohtnunge>.
